    <div class="container">


        <center>

            <div class="container text-center">
                <h1 style="text-align: center;">Take image here from <span style="color: bisque;">SmartCloud AI</span> learning engine ðŸ¤–</h1>
                <p>Here you can generate different photos and test the cloud from the platform.</p>
                <p>Enter text to generate an image:</p>
                <input type="text" id="textInput" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Enter text">
                <button onclick="generateImage()" class="btn btn-primary">Generate Image</button>
                <div id="imageContainer" class="mt-3"></div>
                <button onclick="downloadImage()" id="downloadButton" class="btn btn-success">Download
                    Image</button>
